LanguageData.CWPS.caves.description: Caves are not biomes by themselves but uses the spawnrate of plants for the biome they are in. Some plants have a defined weighting that determines how many of each plant should spawn in relation to other cave plants. For caveplants without a weighting the value is default set to 1.
